    <item>
      <title>退休人员是保守党的最后一道防线，他们急于争取选票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/pensioners-tories-last-line-of-defense-rush-to-secure-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 7 月 4 日选举登记截止日期前的 10 天内，退休人员争相争取选票，这对首相里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 领导的陷入困境的保守党来说是一个可喜的提振。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/pensioners-tories-last-line-of-defense-rush-to-secure-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 16:36:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽森废除犯罪法案，震惊加州政坛</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/newsom-shocks-california-politics-by-scrapping-crime-measure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州州长加文·纽瑟姆 (Gavin Newsom) 突然放弃了一项经过精心谈判、旨在解决财产犯罪和芬太尼危机的投票措施，令该州政界感到震惊，而就在此前一天，州长办公室刚刚大肆宣扬了这项提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/newsom-shocks-california-politics-by-scrapping-crime-measure</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 15:40:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登努力遏制放弃竞选连任的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/biden-faces-mounting-pressure-as-report-says-he-is-weighing-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，《纽约时报》刊登了一篇爆炸性报道称，拜登总统已将退出总统竞选的可能性承认给一位关键盟友，而民主党内部也出现了要求他退出的运动，这进一步加剧了要求拜登总统退出总统竞选的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/biden-faces-mounting-pressure-as-report-says-he-is-weighing-exit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 15:26:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京自五月以来第二次会见习近平，两国领导人高度评价两国关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/putin-meets-xi-for-second-time-since-may-as-leaders-hail-ties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京在不到两个月内第二次会见中国国家主席习近平，大力宣扬俄罗斯与中国的“全面伙伴关系”，凸显莫斯科与北京的深度融合。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/putin-meets-xi-for-second-time-since-may-as-leaders-hail-ties</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 14:42:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列在黎巴嫩南部击毙真主党高级指挥官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/israel-kills-a-hezbollah-senior-commander-in-south-lebanon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列军队在黎巴嫩南部对真主党一名高级指挥官的车辆进行空袭，导致其死亡，这进一步加剧了本已愈演愈烈的敌对局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/israel-kills-a-hezbollah-senior-commander-in-south-lebanon</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 13:14:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基挑战特朗普披露结束战争的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/zelenskiy-challenges-trump-to-reveal-plans-for-quick-end-to-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示，特朗普应该提出尽快结束与俄罗斯战争的计划，并警告称任何提议都必须避免侵犯国家主权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/zelenskiy-challenges-trump-to-reveal-plans-for-quick-end-to-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 11:30:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国汽车城希望工党能启动电动汽车梦想</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/uk-s-motor-city-hopes-labour-can-jump-start-ev-battery-dream</link>
      <description><![CDATA[考文垂市宣布计划在英格兰西米德兰兹郡的小型机场建造一座巨型电动汽车电池工厂，迄今已过去三年多，这给人们带来了希望，即英国能够赶上在电池生产方面已经领先多年的竞争对手国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/uk-s-motor-city-hopes-labour-can-jump-start-ev-battery-dream</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
